column2: "Yo, partner. That girl Matoi isn't with you today?"
"I always see you together these days, so it feels weird when you're not."
"Which reminds me, we were together when we found that girl."

"That Dark Falz... Who seemed to be my older sister.
...That makes twice."
"I'm searching alone, but maybe I have better luck finding people working with you."
"...Well, it's not like she'd listen to me if I found her."
"...Ah, it's useless. Saying things like that now is only going to make me nervous."
"Partner, you didn't give up, even when all of ARKS turned against you. I can't let myself be beaten either."
"Alright, I'm feeling better now. ...Thanks, partner! See you later!"
